{
  "name": "Swin Transformer",
  "description": "Swin Transformer (Microsoft, 2021) — Hierarchical Vision Transformer using Shifted Windows. Computes self-attention within local windows then shifts windows for cross-window connections. Achieves linear complexity vs. quadratic in ViT. State-of-the-art backbone for detection (COCO) and segmentation (ADE20K). CVPR 2022 Best Paper Honorable Mention.",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "dataset-1",
      "type": "Dataset",
